Scope of this license:

This license covers the SPA specification text and accompanying
typographic and visual artifacts in this repository. Adaptations
— implementation guides, vocabulary mappings, training materials,
translations, and other derivative works — are permitted under
the same license, provided attribution to ECCO as the original
steward is preserved and the ShareAlike inheritance carries
through to the derivative.

The architectural principles described in the specification are
offered without proprietary claim, per SPA §10. Firms operating
in the AI governance space are encouraged to publish their own
architecture, ship their own surfaces, and let inspectability be
the credential. Vocabulary alignment, conformance declaration,
and consortium participation are governed by the protocols in
SPA §§7 and §8, not by this license.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Version history of this license file:

  v0.1 / v0.2 of SPA — CC BY-NC-ND 4.0
  v0.3 of SPA onward — CC BY-SA 4.0

The prior CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 terms were superseded in SPA v0.3
because the NonCommercial and NoDerivatives clauses were found
to contradict the Consortium principle (§7's "no commercial moat
at the specification layer" and §4's invitation of vocabulary
mappings as first-class inspectable derivatives). The v0.2 → v0.3
changelog in SPA §8 records this decision in full. Implementations
that built against v0.2 under the prior license remain unaffected;
the change is forward-looking from v0.3 issue.
